This is a macOS app. ALWAYS use Swift 6.0. NEVER use Python, TypeScript, or any other language.

## Platform
- Target: macOS 15.5+ ONLY
- NEVER use UIKit, UIApplication, UIViewController — this is NOT iOS
- Use AppKit instead: NSApplication, NSViewController, NSWindow
- Use UserNotifications for notifications (not UILocalNotification)
- Use AppKit for UI elements: NSButton, NSTextField, NSStackView

## Architecture: MVVM
- Models/ — structs
- ViewModels/ — ObservableObject classes
- Views/ — SwiftUI views
- Services/ — business logic

